{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/2246","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/2246/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/2246/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/2246/events","html_url":"https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/2246","id":3198424644,"node_id":"PR_kwDOLW-eZs6dN-Qb","number":2246,"title":"[toast] Make `Toast.Viewport` an announce container","user":{"login":"atomiks","id":22450188,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIyNDUwMTg4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/22450188?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks","html_url":"https://github.com/atomiks","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":6621343548,"node_id":"LA_kwDOLW-eZs8AAAABiqmvPA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/labels/component:%20toast","name":"component: toast","color":"ffffff","default":false,"description":"Changes related to the toast component."}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":10,"created_at":"2025-07-03T07:51:03Z","updated_at":"2025-07-30T10:27:16Z","closed_at":"2025-07-30T10:27:13Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","issue_field_values":[],"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"draft":false,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/pulls/2246","html_url":"https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/2246","diff_url":"https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/2246.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/2246.patch","merged_at":"2025-07-30T10:27:13Z"},"body":"<!-- Thanks so much for your PR, your contribution is appreciated! ❤️ -->\r\n\r\n- [x] I have followed (at least) the [PR section of the contributing guide](https://github.com/mui/base-ui/blob/HEAD/CONTRIBUTING.md#sending-a-pull-request).\r\n\r\nCurrently the announcer div lives inside the `Toast.Root` as a visually hidden node that has delayed content (since screen readers don't announce content that's inserted with the status node simultaneously, and macOS Safari needs a 'substantial' delay - 50ms was used previously)\r\n\r\nThis makes the `Viewport` act as the announcer and has some possible benefits:\r\n\r\n- Removes timeout/visually hidden hacks.\r\n- Remove `Dialog` `aria-modal` attribute, and instead rely on the `aria-hidden` technique on \"outside\" elements, which ignores `aria-live` elements (the status announcer).\r\n- For low priority toasts, this change also does announce other internal content, which might not be relevant however\r\n- For high priority toasts, they're rendered in a visually hidden container next to the viewport announce container, as they can receive `role=\"alert\"` when dynamically rendered and avoid being announced multiple times in the status container","closed_by":{"login":"atomiks","id":22450188,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIyNDUwMTg4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/22450188?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks","html_url":"https://github.com/atomiks","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/atomiks/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/2246/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/2246/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}